# SCSS Design Tokens

All styling values must come from `palette.scss` tokens. Never hardcode colors, spacing, or radii.

## Import

Every SCSS file must import the palette:

```scss
@import '../palette.scss';   // or ../../palette.scss depending on depth
```

## Colors — use tokens, never raw hex

```scss
// ❌ BAD
background: #fff;
background: #123;
border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
color: #4d9;

// ✅ GOOD
background: $color-bg-app;
background: $color-bg-html;
border: 1px solid $color-border-light;
color: $tertiary-color-light;
```

Brand colors: `$primary-color`, `$secondary-color`, `$tertiary-color`, `$quaternary-color`
Light variants: `$primary-color-light`, `$secondary-color-light`, etc.
Surfaces: `$color-bg-app`, `$color-bg-card-dark`, `$color-bg-button-dark`, `$color-bg-nav-dark`
Text: `$color-text-muted`, `$color-text-muted-dark`, `$color-text-placeholder`, `$color-text-placeholder-dark`
Borders: `$color-border-light`, `$color-border-dark`, `$color-border-card-dark`
Focus: `$color-focus-bg-light`, `$color-focus-bg-dark` with `$tertiary-color-light` / `$tertiary-color`
Error: `$color-input-error`

## Spacing — use scale tokens

```scss
// ❌ BAD
padding: 8px;
gap: 0.75rem;
margin: 2rem;

// ✅ GOOD
padding: $space-sm;       // 0.5rem / 8px
gap: $space-md;           // 0.75rem / 12px
margin: $space-2xl;       // 2rem / 32px
```

Scale: `$space-xs` (4px), `$space-sm` (8px), `$space-md` (12px), `$space-lg` (16px), `$space-xl` (24px), `$space-2xl` (32px), `$space-3xl` (40px)

## Border radius — use scale tokens

```scss
// ❌ BAD
border-radius: 4px;
border-radius: 10px;

// ✅ GOOD
border-radius: $radius-sm;   // 4px — buttons, inputs, cards
border-radius: $radius-xl;   // 10px — modals
```

Scale: `$radius-sm` (4px), `$radius-md` (5px), `$radius-lg` (6px), `$radius-xl` (10px), `$radius-2xl` (12px)

## Dark mode pattern

Always nest dark overrides under `.dark-mode`:

```scss
.my-component {
  background: $color-bg-app;
  color: $dark-color;
}
.dark-mode {
  .my-component {
    background: $color-bg-card-dark;
    color: white;
  }
}
```
